# Getting Started

Welcome to the **@happyvertical/svelte** component library documentation. This library provides a collection of Svelte 5 components for building applications in the HappyVertical ecosystem.

## Installation

```bash
npm install @happyvertical/svelte
# or
pnpm add @happyvertical/svelte
```

